{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782918919623,"sessionID":"ses_0e1c12f14ffe56Cs01FOXHPL99","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"mk-spec-memory_memory_match_triggers","callID":"call_cx9Huru7nX1vqqYkrnCcTilr","state":{"status":"error","input":{"prompt":"You are a deep-review agent running a fan-out lineage.\nThis is an explicit parallel-detached OpenCode lineage, not a self-invocation of the parent session.\nUse the separate lineage directory and session id below as the detached state boundary.\n\n\nRead .opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-review/SKILL.md and execute the review loop with these parameters:\n  spec_folder: .opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/014-skill-doc-drift-audit\n  config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir: .opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/014-skill-doc-drift-audit/review/lineages/gpt-fast-high\n  session_id: fanout-gpt-fast-high-1782918860442-kktrzm\n  executor: cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.5-fast\n  loop_type: review\n  config.stopPolicy: max-iterations\n  config.maxIterations: 10\n  config.convergenceThreshold: 0.1\n\nReview setup bindings (emit before any writes, same as native PRE-BOUND SETUP ANSWERS):\nreview_target: .opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/014-skill-doc-drift-audit\nreview_target_type: spec-folder\nreview_dimensions: all\nspec_folder: .opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/014-skill-doc-drift-audit\nexecution_mode: AUTONOMOUS\nlineage_mode: auto\n\nThe step_resolve_artifact_root step will bind artifact_dir to .opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/014-skill-doc-drift-audit/review/lineages/gpt-fast-high via the\nconfig.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir override — do NOT run the resolveArtifactRoot node\ncommand; bind artifact_dir directly to the override value.\n\nRun phase_init, phase_main_loop (until config.maxIterations is reached; treat convergence before that as telemetry only and broaden review angles instead of synthesizing early), and phase_synthesis.\nWrite all outputs to .opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/014-skill-doc-drift-audit/review/lineages/gpt-fast-high. Do not touch any path outside .opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/014-skill-doc-drift-audit/review/lineages/gpt-fast-high.\n\nWhen complete, output a single line: FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt-fast-high","specFolder":".opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/014-skill-doc-drift-audit","tenantId":"","userId":"","agentId":"","limit":5,"session_id":"fanout-gpt-fast-high-1782918860442-kktrzm","turnNumber":1,"include_cognitive":true},"error":"{\n  \"summary\": \"Error: sessionId \\\"fanout-gpt-fast-high-1782918860442-kktrzm\\\" does not match a server-managed session. Omit sessionId to start a new server-generated session and reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by the server.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"error\": \"sessionId \\\"fanout-gpt-fast-high-1782918860442-kktrzm\\\" does not match a server-managed session. Omit sessionId to start a new server-generated session and reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by the server.\",\n    \"code\": \"E_SESSION_SCOPE\",\n    \"details\": {\n      \"requestedSessionId\": \"fanout-gpt-fast-high-1782918860442-kktrzm\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"hints\": [\n    \"Omit session_id to start a new server-generated session, or reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by memory_context.\"\n  ],\n  \"meta\": {\n    \"tool\": \"memory_match_triggers\",\n    \"tokenCount\": 229,\n    \"cacheHit\": false,\n    \"isError\": true,\n    \"severity\": \"error\",\n    \"tokenBudget\": 3500\n  }\n}","time":{"start":1782918913702,"end":1782918919619}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_08d27c0e7a25b51c016a452ee90eac819b9a7ea20198efd48b"}},"id":"prt_f1e3f3e87001XtMHzAXppeVN4f","sessionID":"ses_0e1c12f14ffe56Cs01FOXHPL99","messageID":"msg_f1e3ed322001e0KboNbBvwU9Q2"}}
