ntation Drift Audit\n\n<!-- SPECKIT_LEVEL: 2 -->\n<!-- SPECKIT_TEMPLATE_SOURCE: tasks-core | v2.2 -->\n\n---\n\n<!-- ANCHOR:phase-1 -->\n## Phase 1: Setup\n\n- [x] T001 Confirmed packet 031 phases 008-013 complete (real behavior exists to audit against).\n- [x] T002 Enumerated 45 candidate skill-doc files via targeted grep across `.opencode/skills` for 031-relevant keywords; recorded in `spec.md` §3.\n- [x] T003 Resolved Gate 3 spec-folder placement with operator: new phase `014-skill-doc-drift-audit` under `031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode`.\n- [x] T004 Resolved verification-timing design with operator: continuous 10-iteration fan-out runs (loop-owned state/locks), not hand-simulated single-iteration mode.\n<!-- /ANCHOR:phase-1 -->\n\n---\n\n<!-- ANCHOR:phase-2 -->\n## Phase 2: Execution\n\n- [x] T005 Launched `fanout-run.cjs --loop-type review` (single lineage `gpt-fast-high`, `cli-opencode openai/gpt-5.5-fast`, `reasoningEffort: high`, `iterations: 10`, `stopPolicy: max-iterations`) against `spec.md`'s candidate file list, review dimensions `all`.\n- [x] T006 Launched `fanout-run.cjs --loop-type research` (same executor/iteration config, `convergenceThreshold: 0.05`) with an explicit `research_topic` describing the same stale-doc investigation, run in parallel with T005.\n- [ ] T007 Wait for both fanouts to reach `phase_synthesis` (review/review-report.md and research/research.md written, or lineage-level synthesis under `review/lineages/gpt-fast-high/` and `research/lineages/gpt-fast-high/`).\n- [ ] T008 Dispatch one fresh Claude Sonnet 5 xhigh agent per written iteration file (20 total: 10 review + 10 research) to independently verify each iteration's findings against real current file content.\n- [ ] T009 Consolidate verified findings into `implementation-summary.md`; flag any finding a verifier could not confirm.\n<!-- /ANCHOR:phase-2 -->\n\n---\n\n<!-- ANCHOR:phase-3 -->\n## Phase 3: Verification\n\n- [ ] T010 Run `validate.sh --strict` on this phase folder.\n- [ ] T011 If stale docs are confirmed, recommend (do not implement) a follow-up fix phase — this phase is findings-only per `spec.md` §3 Out of Scope.\n<!-- /ANCHOR:phase-3 -->","lineStart":1,"lineEnd":61,"totalLines":61,"truncated":false}},"title":".opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/014-skill-doc-drift-audit/tasks.md","time":{"start":1782919014634,"end":1782919014643}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_02ff65c9e4a29610016a452f6691188191851bda46d94a5f2c"}},"id":"prt_f1e4128bf0012oRMEySuN4K83e","sessionID":"ses_0e1c12f14ffe56Cs01FOXHPL99","messageID":"msg_f1e40e5cb001Cbuec0Oz2xm8Q6"}}
